          <li>学术 PPT 配图与演讲封面</li>
          <li>公众号原创封面图生成</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="product-card">
        <div class="product-header">
          <div class="product-icon icon-purple">📝</div>
          <span class="badge badge-gray">● 规划中</span>
        </div>
        <div class="product-name">AI 课题撰写（高端定制）</div>
